data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT! Live | Work | Play! Steps from shopping, brewery,  restaurants, and Stone Mountain Park! 3BD/2.5BA Updated home. Granite countertops. New Carpet. Great for growing family. Oversized master w/ large bonus room. Spacious eat-in kitchen and secondary rooms with walk-in closet. Bay windows in great room. All windows with custom interior shutters. Extra storage galore. Lots of cabinets! Storage room in master and garage! Steps to Stone Mountain Park (walking trails, camping, theme park, and laser show). Co-op broker must accompany buyer at all times. Co-op bonus reduced to 1% if listing agent shows buyer without co-op broker.
